INCLUDE "D:PMG.ACT"››PROC main()››  BYTE ARRAY p0,p1,p2,p3,ms››  BYTE ctr,x››  INT y››  CARD CTR1››  PMGraphics(2)›  p0=PMAdr(0)›  p1=PMAdr(1)›  p2=PMAdr(2)›  p3=PMAdr(3)›  ms=PMAdr(4)›  FOR ctr=0 TO 7›    DO›    PMClear(ctr)›    OD›  FOR ctr=0 TO 7›    DO›    p0(ctr)=$FF›    p1(ctr)=$FF›    p3(ctr)=$FF›    p2(ctr)=$FF›    ms(ctr)=$FF›    OD›  PM_Width(4)=$FF›  FOR ctr=0 TO 3›    DO›    PMColor(ctr,ctr LSH 2,ctr LSH 1)›    OD›  DO›    FOR ctr=0 TO 7›      DO›      x=Rand(160)+48›      y=Rand(96)+16›      PMMove(ctr,x,y)›      OD›  OD›RETURN››››››››